Interface Raytracer.Tweakable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Raytracer.Light, Raytracer.SceneObject
    Enclosing class:
    Raytracer

    static interface Raytracer.Tweakable
    An object that can be an entry in a Raytracer.ListParameter dropdown list. Each instance of a Tweakable has its own set of ParameterControls specific to that instance, which can be obtained with getParameters().

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      java.lang.String getName​()
      Returns a human-friendly String that will identify this object in the dropdown list.
      java.util.ArrayList<Raytracer.ParameterControl> getParameters​()
      Returns a ArrayList of ParameterControls bound to modify this object.
